---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const lastUpdated = "September 15, 2023";
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service - StoryBlog">
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <article class="prose lg:prose-xl">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-purple-900 mb-4">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-purple-600 mb-8">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-purple-900 mb-4">Agreement to Terms</h2>
        <p>
          By accessing and using StoryBlog, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service 
          and our Privacy Policy. If you disagree with any part of these terms, you may not 
          access our service.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-purple-900 mb-4">User Accounts</h2>
        <p>When creating an account, you must:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Provide accurate and complete information</li>
          <li>Maintain the security of your account</li>
          <li>Promptly update any changes to your information</li>
          <li>Accept responsibility for all activities under your account</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-purple-900 mb-4">Content Guidelines</h2>
        <p>Users must not post content that:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Violates any applicable laws</li>
          <li>Infringes on intellectual property rights</li>
          <li>Contains harmful or malicious code</li>
          <li>Harasses, abuses, or threatens others</li>
          <li>Is spam, fraudulent, or misleading</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-purple-900 mb-4">Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>
          The service and its original content (excluding content provided by users) remain 
          the sole property of StoryBlog. Our service is protected by copyright, trademark, 
          and other laws.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-purple-900 mb-4">Termination</h2>
        <p>
          We reserve the right to terminate or suspend access to our service immediately, 
          without prior notice, for any reason including breach of these Terms.
        </p>
      </section>
    </article>
  </main>
</Layout>